OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMostly
OL,6,Fcloudy with further outbreaks of
OL,7,Fmainly light rain, however Orkney
OL,8,Fbecomes dry towards the end of the
OL,9,Fnight and the cloud breaks up.
OL,10,FOccasionally fresh westerly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FEarly cloud and rain across
OL,13,FShetland soon clears, then a bright
OL,14,Fmorning with some sunny spells.
OL,15,FHowever the afternoon looks cloudier
OL,16,Fwith rain, most persistent and
OL,17,Foccasionally heavy across Orkney.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
