OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:
OL,6,FOccasionally heavy, perhaps thundery,
OL,7,Frain early Sunday but becoming drier
OL,8,Fand brighter. Rather cloudy Monday
OL,9,Fwith patchy rain or showers then
OL,10,Fcloudy on Tuesday with occasional
OL,11,Frain. Mainly light winds.
